description:
Welcome to Little Black Dots, where you can follow the notes as you listen. Or you can just sit back and enjoy the music, it's all up to you!

This is Yo-Yo Ma and Emanuel Ax performing Chopin's Introduction and Polonaise brillante in C major, Op. 3.

Please note that this has been uploaded under Law of Fair Use. It is for educational purposes only and no copyrights infringements intended.

Enjoy and Subscribe if you like this!
